<%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Body Start -->
    <div class="container py-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Project Overview</h2>
        <p style="text-align: justify">
            Welcome to DSAVisualizer, where our mission is to simplify the understanding of data structures and
            algorithms through interactive visualizations. Developed with a focus on educational enhancement, our
            platform provides detailed and dynamic visual representations of various algorithms and data structures.
            Whether you're a student, educator, or enthusiast, DSAVisualizer aims to make learning complex algorithms
            engaging and intuitive.
        </p>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section id="about-features" class="text-center py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <!-- Key Features Box -->
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="about-feature-box">
                            <h3>Key Features</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Algorithm Visualization:</strong> Interactive visualizations for searching,
                                    sorting, and other key algorithms.</li>
                                <li><strong>Dynamic Graphs:</strong> Real-time graph-based visualizations to understand
                                    complex data structures.</li>
                                <li><strong>Dynamic Programming (DP):</strong> Visual representations for dynamic
                                    programming solutions to help with problem-solving strategies.</li>
                                <li><strong>Miscellaneous Algorithms:</strong> Additional visual tools for lesser-known
                                    algorithms and techniques.</li>
                                <li><strong>Comprehensive DSA Library:</strong> Extensive library covering a wide range
                                    of data structures and algorithms.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Objectives and Challenges Box -->
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="about-feature-box">
                            <h3>Objectives and Challenges</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Objective:</strong> Enhance understanding of data structures and algorithms
                                    through engaging visual tools and educational content.</li>
                                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Creating clear and accurate visual representations of
                                    complex algorithms and maintaining an intuitive user interface.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Technology Stack Box -->
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="about-feature-box">
                            <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Python, Flask/Django</li>
                                <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, JavaScript, D3.js</li>
                                <li><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL/MySQL</li>
                                <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Custom analytics tools for usage tracking</li>
                                <li><strong>Visualization Libraries:</strong> D3.js, Chart.js</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

